Class Aircraft

  • java.lang.Object
    • aston.group20.model.Aircraft
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAircraft, java.lang.Comparable<IAircraft>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PoweredAircraft, UnpoweredAircraft

    public abstract class Aircraft
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAircraft
    The Aircraft class implements the IAircraft interface and contains the fields and the majority of method implementation; however it still has the two types of Aircraft below it as well as the concrete subclasses.
